      "content": "wow that's a really powerful way to frame it. you're saying that meritocracy is basically just a myth used to keep things the way they are. so, if someone were to argue that wealth redistribution is actually unfair to those who worked hard to build their wealth, how would you counter that in the essay? i want to make sure i can shut down that counterargument effectively.",
